Thanks for the detailled output, it seems your monitor has a bug, the
following patch should fix the problem.

Apply with "patch -p0 < patch_file_name" in ddccontrol/src/lib.

It it works, then send again "LANG= LC_ALL= ddccontrol -p -c -d" so I
could add your monitor to the database.

Best regards,

Nicolas

